  "text": "Delinquent pervert?"
 },
 {
  "i": 50,
  "style": "Hentai",
  "name": "Text-bubbles",
  "text": "{\\frz341\\fs36\\pos(814,394)}Pervert (Hentai)"
 },
 {
  "i": 51,
  "style": "Hentai",
  "name": "Text-bubbles",
  "text": "{\\frz340.9\\fs33\\pos(582,144)}Delinquent (Hikou)"
 },
 {
  "i": 52,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "You mean me?"
 },
 {
  "i": 53,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "They're here!"
 },
 {
  "i": 54,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Here I am! Here!"
 },
 {
  "i": 55,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Welcome!"
 },
 {
  "i": 56,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "A woman? It's a shame, but we were ordered to kill everyone!"
 },
 {
  "i": 57,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Can you kill me?"
 },
 {
  "i": 58,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "What the-?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 59,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Too bad."
 },
 {
  "i": 60,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Mirage Tempo!"
 },
 {
  "i": 61,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Beware of thunderclouds of despair!"
 },
 {
  "i": 62,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Dos Mano"
 },
 {
  "i": 63,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Clutch!"
 },
 {
  "i": 64,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Split-Hoof"
 },
 {
  "i": 65,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Diamond!"
 },
 {
  "i": 66,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Don't break formation!"
 },
 {
  "i": 67,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "I knew it, they're calling for me."
 },
 {
  "i": 68,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Now!"
 },
 {
  "i": 69,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Huh? They didn't mean me?"
 },
 {
  "i": 70,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "What?! Bullets don't affect him?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 71,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Strong Hammer!"
 },
 {
  "i": 72,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "Amazing! They're all really strong, Pappag!"
 },
 {
  "i": 73,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "To think they'd go this far..."
 },
 {
  "i": 74,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "We were just gonna grab Hachi and escape..."
 },
 {
  "i": 75,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Take this!"
 },
 {
  "i": 76,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Damn! Franky! We need to get the ship ashore!"
 },
 {
  "i": 77,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "They're at an advantage out here in the ocean!"
 },
 {
  "i": 78,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "That's probably why they live out here, you know."
 },
 {
  "i": 79,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "They're not gonna give us a chance to steer the ship!"
 },
 {
  "i": 80,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 81,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Run! A huge guy is coming!"
 },
 {
  "i": 82,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hachi",
  "text": "Is it the Iron Mask?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 83,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "The masked guy and a cow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 84,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "A cow?"
 },
 {
  "i": 85,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "That's Motobaro's voice!"
 },
 {
  "i": 86,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "It's the Head!"
 },
 {
  "i": 87,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Getting yourselves knocked down in droves..."
 },
 {
  "i": 88,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What's that?! Something showed up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 89,
  "style": "Captions",
  "name": "",
  "text": "{\\fad(500,0)\\fs32}Duval's\\NBeloved Bison\\N{\\r}Motobaro"
 },
 {
  "i": 90,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "You're not just bugs, y'know! Flying Fish Riders!"
 },
 {
  "i": 91,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "H-He crushed his own house..."
 },
 {
  "i": 92,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I don't need this base any more, as long as I can kill the Straw Hats!"
 },
 {
  "i": 93,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "We're so sorry, Head! We'll draw them out to sea and finish them off right..."
 },
 {
  "i": 94,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Move it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 95,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I have no need for a fishman, mermaid, or glove! If you wanna run, then just get lost!"
 },
 {
  "i": 96,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "I'm a starfish!"
 },
 {
  "i": 97,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I didn't enter the slave-trading market 'cause I wanted to!"
 },
 {
  "i": 98,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "You guys understand that, right?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 99,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "Of course, Head!"
 },
 {
  "i": 100,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "What a great day this is!"
 },
 {
  "i": 101,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "The man whom I wanted to kill so badly that I even saw him in my dreams, is right here."
 },
 {
  "i": 102,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I'm so grateful!"
 },
 {
  "i": 103,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I guess there is a god, huh?"
 },
 {
  "i": 104,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "One day, I was suddenly thrown into the depths of hell because of that man!"
 },
 {
  "i": 105,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Hey, isn't he looking at us while he's talking?"
 },
 {
  "i": 106,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Today, I'll kill ya right here, even if I die myself..."
 },
 {
  "i": 107,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Pirate... Black Leg Sanji!"
 },
 {
  "i": 108,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I really wanted to meet'cha!"
 },
 {
  "i": 109,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Oh, crap! The Head's really pissed off!"
 },
 {
  "i": 110,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Me? That guy wants to kill me?"
 },
 {
  "i": 111,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Sanji, who's that guy?"
 },
 {
  "i": 112,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "It seems like he's got some sort of grudge against you..."
 },
 {
  "i": 113,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Could it be something that happened at the restaurant? Try to remember!"
 },
 {
  "i": 114,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "If it's something from back then, I did plenty of things that people might be mad at me for..."
 },
 {
  "i": 115,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Let him shoot you! You've deserved it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 116,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Quit playin' dumb, Black Leg!"
 },
 {
  "i": 117,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "We're talkin' about somethin' recent here!"
 },
 {
  "i": 118,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Crap! Those are harpoons!"
 },
 {
  "i": 119,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "But if it's something recent, then I'm even more confused!"
 },
 {
  "i": 120,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "W-What? There's something strange about these harpoons..."
 },
 {
  "i": 121,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "These're my scorpion venom harpoons!"
 },
 {
  "i": 122,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "If they hit'cha, ya'll be headed for the afterlife in three minutes!"
 },
 {
  "i": 123,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Know the depths of my fury!"
 },
 {
  "i": 124,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Nami-san, watch out!"
 },
 {
  "i": 125,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Damn bastard, I can't remember at all! Who are you?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 126,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I'm gonna kill ya and yer crew!"
 },
 {
  "i": 127,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I saw what was underneath that mask."
 },
 {
  "i": 128,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Really? Who is he?"
 },
 {
  "i": 129,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Don't be surprised. You've seen his face too!"
 },
 {
  "i": 130,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Me too?"
 },
 {
  "i": 131,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "That bastard...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 132,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "He knocked off Duval-sama's iron mask!"
 },
 {
  "i": 133,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Very well... Take a close look at my scarred face!"
 },
 {
  "i": 134,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What the-?!?!?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 135,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "No way!"
 },
 {
  "i": 136,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "He's...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 137,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "My..."
 },
 {
  "i": 138,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Oh, my..."
 },
 {
  "i": 139,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "I wanna cry!"
 },
 {
  "i": 140,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I've been waitin' for this day..."
 },
 {
  "i": 141,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I decided to murder ya, and so I set out to sea!"
 },
 {
  "i": 142,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "But lookin' for ya would be a problem, y'know..."
 },
 {
  "i": 143,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "After all, yer wanted poster and yer true face didn't match!"
 },
 {
  "i": 144,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Even if the marines or bounty hunters ran into ya, they just might' not notice ya!"
 },
 {
  "i": 145,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Nah, there's no way that'd happen!"
 },
 {
  "i": 146,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Those guys'd definitely find ya!"
 },
 {
  "i": 147,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "Head...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 148,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "They'd find ya, and then they'd say..."
 },
 {
  "i": 149,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "\"Found you!\""
 },
 {
  "i": 150,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "\"Black Leg Sanji!\""
 },
 {
  "i": 151,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "And then I'd tell 'em..."
 },
 {
  "i": 152,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "\"I dunno anyone like that!\""
 },
 {
  "i": 153,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "\"I ain't even a pirate!\""
 },
 {
  "i": 154,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Hey, Sanji, where are you going?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 155,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Do ya realise..."
 },
 {
  "i": 156,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "How frightenin' it was, suddenly bein' targeted by bounty hunters?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 157,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Why?"
 },
 {
  "i": 158,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Why'd I suddenly have to be chased by the Navy HQ?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 159,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Why'd all those big name bounty hunters suddenly start huntin' me?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 160,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Why?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 161,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Sanji?"
 },
 {
  "i": 162,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "What'd I do?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 163,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Give me my life back!"
 },
 {
  "i": 164,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Black Leg Sanji!"
 },
 {
  "i": 165,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Like I care!"
 },
 {
  "i": 166,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "Head!"
 },
 {
  "i": 167,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Whaddaya mean, \"Like I care\"?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 168,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "If ya ain't gonna take responsibility for dis, then who will?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 169,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 170,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I'm more pissed about that wanted-poster than anyone!"
 },
 {
  "i": 171,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "So, things like this really can happen, huh?"
 },
 {
  "i": 172,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "What a surprise..."
 },
 {
  "i": 173,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "This world is really big."
 },
 {
  "i": 174,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Was Sanji born under some kind of miracle-star or something?"
 },
 {
  "i": 175,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "He might meet quite an interesting end someday..."
 },
 {
  "i": 176,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "I can't help but feel sorry for that Duval guy..."
 },
 {
  "i": 177,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hachi",
  "text": "Those two look exactly like each other!"
 },
 {
  "i": 178,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Like two peas in a pod."
 },
 {
  "i": 179,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Brook! I'm so gonna kick the crap out of you afterwards!"
 },
 {
  "i": 180,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Well then, Sanji..."
 },
 {
  "i": 181,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "We'll just be going on ahead."
 },
 {
  "i": 182,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Are you saying this is my fault?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 183,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "If you don't want to look like that wanted picture, you could just change your hairstyle or your beard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 184,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "There are plenty of things you could just change!"
 },
 {
  "i": 185,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "So I could have done that?"
 },
 {
  "i": 186,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Are you all morons?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 187,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "We're not morons!"
 },
 {
  "i": 188,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "You know, Black Leg, we..."
 },
 {
  "i": 189,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "We..."
 },
 {
  "i": 190,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Were running a small, unknown mafia in some distant corner of this sea..."
 },
 {
  "i": 191,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "We spent every single day by threatening the villagers for money..."
 },
 {
  "i": 192,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "That was the kind of happy life we had."
 },
 {
  "i": 193,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Black Leg..."
 },
 {
  "i": 194,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Do you understand?"
 },
 {
  "i": 195,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I, who had never caused any kind of uproar..."
 },
 {
  "i": 196,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Suddenly found myself with a bounty of 77 million..."
 },
 {
  "i": 197,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "And was chased around by those powerful marines..."
 },
 {
  "i": 198,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I got this nasty scar on my back,"
 },
 {
  "i": 199,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "and was forced to wear this iron mask to hide my face from the world!"
 },
 {
  "i": 200,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "It's yer fault dat my life was ruined!"
 },
 {
  "i": 201,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I'm prepared to chase ya to da ends of Hell!"
 },
 {
  "i": 202,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "If dat's a problem for ya..."
 },
 {
  "i": 203,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Then how about you just kill me right now?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 204,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I'm bein' killed!"
 },
 {
  "i": 205,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Those stupid accusations of yours..."
 },
 {
  "i": 206,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Why'd you even have to put Nami-san and Robin-chan in danger?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 207,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "It's dat ship and dat crew dat made ya a famous pirate!"
 },
 {
  "i": 208,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Of course I'd want revenge on'em!"
 },
 {
  "i": 209,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Ya guys should all die!"
 },
 {
  "i": 210,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Poison harpoons?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 211,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Get in formation!"
 },
 {
  "i": 212,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Huh?"
 },
 {
  "i": 213,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Oh, crap!"
 },
 {
  "i": 214,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Sanji-kun!"
 },
 {
  "i": 215,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "They're trying to pull him down into the ocean!"
 },
 {
  "i": 216,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Sanji! Hurry up and get out of there!"
 },
 {
  "i": 217,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Damn, this net is made of steel!"
 },
 {
  "i": 218,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Now suffer and drown!"
 },
 {
  "i": 219,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Sanji!"
 },
 {
  "i": 220,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Dammit... I'll save you right now!"
 },
 {
  "i": 221,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Don't go there yourself, idiot! I'll go get him!"
 },
 {
  "i": 222,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hachi",
  "text": "Wait!"
 },
 {
  "i": 223,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hachi",
  "text": "You humans are too slow, you can't catch him!"
 },
 {
  "i": 224,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Hachi",
  "text": "Leave this to me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 225,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Fool!"
 },
 {
  "i": 226,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "You fishmen don't stand a chance at catching up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 227,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "The Flying Fish are the fastest animals in the sea!"
 },
 {
  "i": 228,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "And the Riders riding them have air canisters, so they can stay under water for as long as they like!"
 },
 {
  "i": 229,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "That guy doesn't stand a chance!"
 },
 {
  "i": 230,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "The next time that guy, Black Leg surfaces..."
 },
 {
  "i": 231,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "He'll already have drowned and died!"
 },
 {
  "i": 232,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "What was that!?"
 },
 {
  "i": 233,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Feel the Head's anger, Black Leg!"
 },
 {
  "i": 234,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Can't breathe..."
 },
 {
  "i": 235,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "It's okay!"
 },
 {
  "i": 236,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Camie!"
 },
 {
  "i": 237,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "Hey, cowboy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 238,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "It seems that you forgot someone here!"
 },
 {
  "i": 239,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Huh?"
 },
 {
  "i": 240,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "The Flying Fish are most certainly faster than fishmen."
 },
 {
  "i": 241,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "They're in the top-class among sea-creatures. They really are something!"
 },
 {
  "i": 242,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "However..."
 },
 {
  "i": 243,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "The creatures at the very top of that top-class are the merfolk!"
 },
 {
  "i": 244,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "In this great sea..."
 },
 {
  "i": 245,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "There are no creatures that can outrun a mermaid under water!"
 },
 {
  "i": 246,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "It's alright..."
 },
 {
  "i": 247,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "I'll save you right now, Sanji-chin!"
 },
 {
  "i": 248,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Is she really that incredible?"
 },
 {
  "i": 249,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pappag",
  "text": "Actually, if she hadn't been spacing out all the time, nobody would ever catch her!"
 },
 {
  "i": 250,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I see..."
 },
 {
  "i": 251,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Camie!"
 },
 {
  "i": 252,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Take care of Sanji!"
 },
 {
  "i": 253,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "What's that?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 254,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "A huge anchor?"
 },
 {
  "i": 255,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "It's way too huge!"
 },
 {
  "i": 256,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Aim for the Straw Hat crew's ship."
 },
 {
  "i": 257,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Hit it head-on and sink it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 258,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Some of'em are Devil Fruit users!\\NIf we get'em into the water, they're ours!"
 },
 {
  "i": 259,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "This is bad! Just one hit from that and we'll sink!"
 },
 {
  "i": 260,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Dodge it! Use the Burst or the Paddle! Can we make it?"
 },
 {
  "i": 261,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "No, it's too late!"
 },
 {
  "i": 262,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Hurry and come with me, Usopp!"
 },
 {
  "i": 263,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Huh?"
 },
 {
  "i": 264,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Y-Yeah!"
 },
 {
  "i": 265,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "You get on the bow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 266,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Huh?"
 },
 {
  "i": 267,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Uh, right!"
 },
 {
  "i": 268,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "We're gonna use our secret weapon!"
 },
 {
  "i": 269,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Secret weapon?"
 },
 {
  "i": 270,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Drop it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 271,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "The Sunny's in trouble!"
 },
 {
  "i": 272,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "That thing is dangerous!"
 },
 {
  "i": 273,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Believe in this ship!"
 },
 {
  "i": 274,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "The mane started spinning!"
 },
 {
  "i": 275,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Sink!"
 },
 {
  "i": 276,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It's falling right at us!"
 },
 {
  "i": 277,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Emergency Evasion..."
 },
 {
  "i": 278,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Secret Weapon!"
 },
 {
  "i": 279,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Chicken Voyage!"
 },
 {
  "i": 280,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Riders",
  "text": "They dodged it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 281,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "No way!"
 },
 {
  "i": 282,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "I've never heard of any ship that can go backwards!"
 },
 {
  "i": 283,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Usopp!"
 },
 {
  "i": 284,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Get inside the prow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 285,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "The prow?"
 },
 {
  "i": 286,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Woah! You can enter it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 287,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Don't think dodging it was all we could do!"
 },
 {
  "i": 288,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "This ship has got way more power than that!"
 },
 {
  "i": 289,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper & Luffy",
  "text": "Awesome!"
 },
 {
  "i": 290,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "What is it now?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 291,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Charging complete!"
 },
 {
  "i": 292,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Hey!"
 },
 {
  "i": 293,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What should I do now?"
 },
 {
  "i": 294,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Get as many as you can inside the circle!"
 },
 {
  "i": 295,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Circle?"
 },
 {
  "i": 296,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Like this?"
 },
 {
  "i": 297,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "They're in!"
 },
 {
  "i": 298,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Lock on with the button on the handle, then pull the lever!"
 },
 {
  "i": 299,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "This and..."
 },
 {
  "i": 300,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "This?"
 },
 {
  "i": 301,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "What's that?"
 },
 {
  "i": 302,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Gaon: Lion's roar"
 },
 {
  "i": 303,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Gaon Cannon!"
 },
 {
  "i": 304,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky & Usopp",
  "text": "Fire!"
 },
 {
  "i": 305,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Amazing!"
 },
 {
  "i": 306,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "You're too impressed!"
 },
 {
  "i": 307,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Did you see that?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 308,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "The Sunny's full power?"
 },
 {
  "i": 309,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "That move took out almost all the Flying Fish!"
 },
 {
  "i": 310,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "That's just how good Usopp is!"
 },
 {
  "i": 311,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "For a first try it was magnificent!"
 },
 {
  "i": 312,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Wow!!! What an amazing destructive power!"
 },
 {
  "i": 313,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Sunny!"
 },
 {
  "i": 314,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Lion-chan is incredible! It seemed as if my eyes were going to pop out!"
 },
 {
  "i": 315,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Though I have no eyes to pop out..."
 },
 {
  "i": 316,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "It uses three barrels of cola to prevent the ship from being blown away..."
 },
 {
  "i": 317,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "And at the same time, it releases two barrels worth of Coup de Burst from the cannon."
 },
 {
  "i": 318,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "It uses a ton of cola, so don't you overuse it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 319,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "She's tied us up with the net!"
 },
 {
  "i": 320,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "Damn!"
 },
 {
  "i": 321,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Rider",
  "text": "That speedy mermaid!"
 },
 {
  "i": 322,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "We're almost there, Sanji-chin..."
 },
 {
  "i": 323,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "Hang in there!"
 },
 {
  "i": 324,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Camie!"
 },
 {
  "i": 325,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Thank goodness!"
 },
 {
  "i": 326,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Is Sanji all right?"
 },
 {
  "i": 327,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "Everyone, it's terrible!"
 },
 {
  "i": 328,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "Sanji-chin is losing a lot of blood!"
 },
 {
  "i": 329,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Huh?"
 },
 {
  "i": 330,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Did he get done in?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 331,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "Just when I thought I'd saved him, a lot of blood suddenly started flowing out of his nose!"
 },
 {
  "i": 332,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Nosebleed?"
 },
 {
  "i": 333,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It's fine..."
 },
 {
  "i": 334,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "If he dies like that, then let him die."
 },
 {
  "i": 335,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "That's true..."
 },
 {
  "i": 336,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "At least he seems happy."
 },
 {
  "i": 337,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Camie",
  "text": "Hang in there, Sanji-chin!"
 },
 {
  "i": 338,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Is this..."
 },
 {
  "i": 339,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Heaven?"
 },
 {
  "i": 340,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Damn..."
 },
 {
  "i": 341,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "He survived, huh?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 342,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Well, it looks like your subordinates are useless now, doesn't it?"
 },
 {
  "i": 343,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Why, you...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 344,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Then, I guess you should learn how terrifying Motobaro is!"
 },
 {
  "i": 345,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I've lost count of how many fools have been impaled by his giant horns to this day!"
 },
 {
  "i": 346,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "They say his horns have even managed to destroy village dams..."
 },
 {
  "i": 347,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Put him in a cage, and he'll break straight out!"
 },
 {
  "i": 348,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "The only reason I've been able to escape from the Navy all this time..."
 },
 {
  "i": 349,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Is because of this guy's horns!"
 },
 {
  "i": 350,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "They call them the \"Heart-smashing horns\"!"
 },
 {
  "i": 351,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "All right."
 },
 {
  "i": 352,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I'll stop you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 353,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Go, Motobaro!"
 },
 {
  "i": 354,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Watch out, Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 355,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "The horns were completely useless!"
 },
 {
  "i": 356,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "There's no point in us fighting!"
 },
 {
  "i": 357,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Hey, what's wrong, Motobaro?"
 },
 {
  "i": 358,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "The cow's acting strangely, isn't it?"
 },
 {
  "i": 359,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "What?"
 },
 {
  "i": 360,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "He lost consciousness?"
 },
 {
  "i": 361,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "What just happened?"
 },
 {
  "i": 362,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 363,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Nami",
  "text": "What did you do?"
 },
 {
  "i": 364,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I didn't do anything!"
 },
 {
  "i": 365,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Motobaro!"
 },
 {
  "i": 366,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Damn, how can this be?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 367,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "It doesn't seem like he attacked it..."
 },
 {
  "i": 368,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Robin",
  "text": "It seems like Luffy won the cow over by talking to it..."
 },
 {
  "i": 369,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What?"
 },
 {
  "i": 370,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You mean, he psyched it out?"
 },
 {
  "i": 371,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "But that huge thing just fainted!"
 },
 {
  "i": 372,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Is that even possible?"
 },
 {
  "i": 373,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Why, you... Damn Straw Hat kid...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 374,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Hey, wait a minute, Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 375,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Sanji!"
 },
 {
  "i": 376,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I'm glad you're alright!"
 },
 {
  "i": 377,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I'll end this stupid incident filled with pointless accusations myself!"
 },
 {
  "i": 378,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Finish it?"
 },
 {
  "i": 379,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "Black Leg!"
 },
 {
  "i": 380,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "As long as you keep on living as a pirate I'll never find peace!"
 },
 {
  "i": 381,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Duval",
  "text": "I'm the one who's sick of the accusations!"
 },
 {
  "i": 382,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 383,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I don't want to see that stupid poster-face any more than you do."
 },
 {
  "i": 384,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "It shouldn't even exist in real life!"
 },
 {
  "i": 385,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Well, then..."
 },
 {
  "i": 386,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "",
  "text": "You should just die!"
 },
 {
